               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440408-name-939" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-939" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-939" type="surname" value="SOAMES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-939" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES SOAMES</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> Turner swore she picked up a pin—this is the one that I saw the prisoner take out of his shirt and throw down—it is not the prosecutor's pin she swore to.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440408-name-940" type="witnessName">
